{
  "page": "Feature quote/182",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p>“Your mother was a <a href=\"/index.php/Septa\" title=\"Septa\">septa</a>. <a href=\"/index.php/Oberyn_Martell\" title=\"Oberyn Martell\">Oberyn</a> once told me that she read to you in the cradle from the <a href=\"/index.php/Seven-Pointed_Star\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Seven-Pointed Star\">Seven-Pointed Star</a>. I want you in <a href=\"/index.php/King%27s_Landing\" title=\"King&#39;s Landing\">King's Landing</a> too, but on the <a href=\"/index.php/Visenya%27s_Hill\" title=\"Visenya&#39;s Hill\">other hill</a>. The <a href=\"/index.php/Warrior%27s_Sons\" title=\"Warrior&#39;s Sons\">Swords</a> and the <a href=\"/index.php/Poor_Fellows\" title=\"Poor Fellows\">Stars</a> have been re-formed, and this new <a href=\"/index.php/High_Sparrow\" title=\"High Sparrow\">High Septon</a> is not the puppet that the others were. Try and get close to him.” —<a href=\"/index.php/Doran_Martell\" title=\"Doran Martell\">Doran Martell</a><br />“Why not? White suits my coloring. I look so . . . pure.” —<a href=\"/index.php/Tyene_Sand\" title=\"Tyene Sand\">Tyene Sand</a><sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwd38.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwd38.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></p><div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Radwd38.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Radwd38.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Dance_with_Dragons\" title=\"A Dance with Dragons\">A Dance with Dragons</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Dance_with_Dragons-Chapter_38\" title=\"A Dance with Dragons-Chapter 38\">Chapter 38</a>, The Watcher.</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260405101836\nCache expiry: 1209600\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.008 seconds\nReal time usag